{"tid":1796053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"是日離地撚：邱騰華","createTime":"2019-12-24T10:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T12:27:35.000Z","uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9898257414637b1e83330d44fdb0b24f5da6e63","tid":1796053,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:54:32.000Z","msg":"而家社會環境，黃藍是否能同一枱食飯已成疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華今日於商業電台節目《在晴朗的一天出發》中質疑「黃色經濟圈」是否可持續，以及是否適合香港社會。他又舉例稱，「一家人去食飯，係唔係要分兩間酒樓？」邱說不相信香港是如此分化的社會。<br />\n<br />\n來源hk01"},{"pid":"f35b0f391e0ac16803a7ac0368fb06e41cd9bd83","tid":1796053,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T11:18:32.000Z","msg":"一家大小去食飯<br />\n以區選結果為參考<br />\n9黃：1藍<br />\n100%去食黃店"},{"pid":"801ab0bd00d18de76161e1a9c18a5b337af31e40","tid":1796053,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T12:27:35.000Z","msg":"邱說不相信香港是如此分化的社會。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}